  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients 18 years of age or older

          -  Signs or symptoms of HF

          -  Able and willing to provide freely given written informed consent including analysis
             of genomics

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with acute myocardial infarction

          -  Recent trauma or surgery (&lt; 3 months)

          -  Hemodynamically significant valvular disease

          -  Serious cerebrovascular disease or stroke in the last 3 months

          -  Chronic dialysis

          -  Chronic liver disease

          -  Chronic infectious (bacterial or viral) disease

          -  Any malignant concomitant diseases or a malignant disease in the last 5 years

          -  Systemic inflammatory diseases, such as autoimmune diseases, connective tissue
             diseases or collagenoses

          -  Pregnant women
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
